      "message": "SkSafeMath safe;\n    const auto glyphsSize \u003d safe.mul(glyphCount, sizeof(uint16_t)),\n                  posSize \u003d safe.mul(safe.mul(glyphCount, sizeof(SkScalar)), ScalarsPerGlyph(pos)),\n              clusterSize \u003d pe.extended ? safe.mul(glyphCount * sizeof(uint32_t)) : 0,\n                totalSize \u003d safe.add(glyphsSize, safe.add(posSize, safe.add(clusterSize, textSize)));\n\n\n    SkDEBUGCODE(const auto expectedOffset \u003d reader.offset() + totalSize);\n    if (!reader.isValid() || !safe || totalSize \u003e reader.available()) {\n        return nullptr;\n    }",
